Package: openhrv
Title: Open Heart Rate Variability Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Open",
           family = "HRV",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "openhrv@example.org")
Description: Open, reproducible heart rate variability analysis for
    scientists. The package starts from RR or NN intervals, performs
    artifact screening and correction, computes time-domain,
    frequency-domain, geometric, and nonlinear HRV metrics, and can
    generate simple reports.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
